      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the potato is golden, remove the tray[s] from the oven and top with the <strong>torn</strong> <strong>ciabatta</strong></p><p>Top with a generous drizzle of <strong>olive</strong> <strong>oil</strong>, then return the tray[s] to the oven for a further 7-8 min or until golden and crisp</p>",
      "order": 5,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-5-1714492571324-x200.jpg",
