      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, combine your <strong>mayo</strong> and <strong>white wine vinegar</strong> in a large bowl with your <strong>dried</strong> <strong>oregano</strong>, 2 tbsp <span class=\"text-purple\">[3 tbsp] </span><span class=\"text-danger\">[4 tbsp]</span> <strong>olive oil</strong> and a pinch of <strong>salt</strong>, <strong>pepper </strong>and <strong>sugar</strong> – this is your <strong>creamy dressing</strong></p>",
      "order": 6,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-6-1714492574017-x200.jpg",
