      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add the <strong>torn</strong> <strong>lettuce</strong> and <strong>shredded inner core</strong> to the bowl of dressing with the <strong>tomato</strong> <strong>wedges</strong> and a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and give everything a good mix up – this is your <strong>salad</strong></p>",
      "order": 7,
